msgctxt "804"
msgid "Silver-Tongued Hostess"
msgstr "Hostess persuasiva"

msgctxt "808"
msgid "Businessman with a Thinning Wallet"
msgstr "Empresario con poco dinero"

msgctxt "84_Silver-Tongued Hostess"
msgid "This moneylender's been in one mess after another. I think it's called Sky Finance."
msgstr "Ese prestamista siempre anda en problemas. Creo que la empresa se llama Sky Finance."

msgctxt "96_Businessman with a Thinning Wallet"
msgid "Yeah, I heard about that murder from a bit ago."
msgstr "Sí, escuché que hubo un asesinato hace un tiempo."

msgctxt "108_Silver-Tongued Hostess"
msgid "Hmm... Maybe it was money problems? Just shows you shouldn't take out a loan from this kind of place."
msgstr "Mmm... ¿Tal vez problemas con dinero? Queda claro que hay que evitar pedir préstamos en este tipo de sitios."

msgctxt "120_Businessman with a Thinning Wallet"
msgid "Yeah... I think the problem is more with murder than their ability to finance a loan..."
msgstr "Eh... Sospecho que el problema real son los homicidios, no su gestión crediticia..."

